These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, polish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, skateboard
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the polish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | polish    | russian |
| Sport         | biathlon | handball    |
| Transport     | bus     | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, french
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the mexican is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | lemonade   |
| Nationality   | french | mexican  |
| Transport     | tram   | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, gardening
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, action
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, climbing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | singing   | gardening  |
| Movie-Genre   | action | crime  |
| Sport         | basketball   | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: orange, nectarine
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person eating orange is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | orange | nectarine |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | martial-arts   |
| Transport     | roller       | helicopter      |

