.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, lime
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, pilot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | lime | pineapple     |
| Job     | pilot | writer |
| Sport   | volleyball | tennis    |

 #################################

 
