.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, broccoli
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, singing
2 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | broccoli | cranberry  |
| Hobby   | singing | collecting |
| Pet     | bird  | hedgehog     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, skydiving
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, australian
2 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading |
| Nationality   | egyptian     | australian     |
| Pet           | hamster          | turtle     |

 #################################

 
