.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, hip-hop
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, tram
1. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | hip-hop  |
| Transport     | tram | taxi    |

 